"baliL' (R t1 a (R t2 b t3)) _ c t4 = R (B t1 a t2) b (rightredB t3 c t4)" |
"baliL' (R (R t1 a t2) b t3) _ c t4 = R (B t1 a t2) b (rightredB t3 c t4)" |
